on notice regarding financial assistance and rehabilitation of affected people of village Chatorkhand and Dine Ghizer District</td><td></td></tr><tr><td> </td><td colspan="2"><strong>Resolutions passed in 5th session ( 2nd June to 11th June, 2010)</strong></td></tr><tr><td>11</td><td>Resolution regarding write-off ZTBL loans upto Rs. 50000/- in Gilgit-Baltistan.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>12</td><td>Resolution regarding regularization of contract employees working in different departments of Gilgit-Baltistan.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>13</td><td>Resolution regarding condemnation of Israil, aggression at Freedom Fortilla.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td>Resolution regarding condemnation of blasphemous caricatures of Holly Prophet (PBUH).</td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td colspan="2"><strong>Session Held from 26th July, to 2nd August, 2010 has passed the Following Resolutions.</strong></td></tr><tr><td>15</td><td>Resolution of condemnation trespass of Boundary Line of Gilgit-Baltistan at Basiry Check Post by the leaders of Tahrik-e-Hazara Movement.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>16</td><td>Resolution regarding condemnation of Indian claim on construction of Diamer Basha Dam.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>17</td><td>Resolution regarding condemnation of continuous terrorist attack in the Country.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>18</td><td>Resolution regarding delegation of powers to the Gilgit-Baltistan Legislative Assembly to make amendments in the (Gilgit-Baltistan Empowerment and Self Governance Order, 2009).</td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td colspan="2"><strong>Session held from 1st October, 2010</strong></td></tr><tr><td>19</td><td>Resolution regarding condemnation of terrorist attack on the innocent persons at Basin Gilgit.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td colspan="2"><strong>Session held from 4th Feburary, 2011</strong></td></tr><tr><td>20</td><td>Resolution regarding Thanks to President of Pakistan Mr. Asif Ali Zardari and Prime Minister of Pakistan Mr. Syed Yousaf Raz